<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.com/2020/8/off-white-black-white-half-half-sneaker-derby-mismatched-shoe-pack-drop-virgil-abloh">Off-White 重新定义什么是「一双鞋」</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1361510" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/11-4.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="854" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/11-4.jpg 1280w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/11-4-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/11-4-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/11-4-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<p>Hypebeast 消息，潮牌 Off-White 推出一双两边不同的球鞋 Black and White Half-Half —— 看起来就是一边是球鞋，一边是德比鞋。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1361511" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/22-1.jpg" alt="" width="880" height="587" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/22-1.jpg 880w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/22-1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/22-1-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px" /></p>
<p>但如果细看，我们能看到两边鞋的鞋垫、鞋底等元素都是相同的，因此穿起来的体验应该没有想象中不舒服。这款球鞋的定价为 605 美元（约合人民币 4200 元）。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.stanley-pmi.com/shop/classic-perfect-brew-pour-over-set">Stanley 推出免滤纸手冲咖啡套装</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1361512" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-8.jpg" alt="" width="858" height="605" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-8.jpg 858w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-8-360x254.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-8-768x542.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 858px) 100vw, 858px" /></p>
<p>老牌保温壶品牌 Stanley 推出了一款便携手冲咖啡套装，自带过滤芯，不需咖啡滤纸，操作简易。此外，套装的主要材料为不锈钢，坚固耐用，甚至合适带到户外露营时使用。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1361513" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2-9.jpg" alt="" width="927" height="492" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2-9.jpg 927w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2-9-360x191.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2-9-768x408.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 927px) 100vw, 927px" /></p>
<p>除了可搭配原有的不锈钢马克杯，用户还可将过滤器用于一般马克杯，或者配合 Stanley 的标准保温壶使用。套装定价为 35 美元（约人民币 242 元）。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%BB%B4%E6%BB%B4%E8%BF%914%E6%88%90%E6%80%A7%E9%AA%9A%E6%89%B0%E4%B8%BA%E7%94%B7%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E9%AA%9A%E6%89%B0%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%B8%E6%9C%BA%23&amp;Refer=top">滴滴发布第二季度醉酒报告</a></h4>
<p>滴滴公示了 2020 年第二季度网约车乘客醉酒引发的车内冲突和性骚扰数据。</p>
<p>醉酒投诉性骚扰中，女乘客投诉男司机性骚扰同比下降 42.9%；97.7% 是司机投诉乘客。综合来看，男司机投诉男乘客占比最高，以 36.8% 的比率略高于女司机投诉男乘客的 36.3%。</p>
<p>网友：「男人何苦为难男人啊。」「酒品见人品，望酒局下各位自重。」「这个男女是怎么看的？因为我就是女的，但我资料性别为男，头像是我爸。」</p>
<h4><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357583" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h4>
<h4>贾樟柯首次艺术个展：《面 MIÀN》</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1361389" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/t01ba6b4cf383a9d75f.png" alt="" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/t01ba6b4cf383a9d75f.png 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/t01ba6b4cf383a9d75f-360x203.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/t01ba6b4cf383a9d75f-768x432.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/t01ba6b4cf383a9d75f-1024x576.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/11/72x72/1f4cd.png" alt="📍" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> 地址：Prada 荣宅（上海）/ 小程序</p>
<p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/11/72x72/231b.png" alt="⌛" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> 时间：8 月 31 日 &#8211; 9 月 1 日</p>
<p>作为 Prada Mode 文化俱乐部第五站活动，Prada 联手贾樟柯推出主题为《面 MIÀN》的活动。活动将以「吃面」「表面」和「会面」三个维度开展。</p>
<p><iframe src="https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=j3142xr71tc" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p>
<p>▲ 活动主题视频</p>
<p>「吃面」为品尝汾阳传统面食，灵感源自荣宅历史（「面粉大王」荣宗敬的家宅）和贾樟柯导演在山西开设的「山河故人・家厨」；「表面」则将呈现贾樟柯导演的摄影和装置作品，并打造 90 年代迪斯科的音乐派对；「会面」则是对话，贾樟柯将分别和不同嘉宾进行对话，围绕文学、电影、建筑等主题展开对谈。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1361390" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/talks.jpg" alt="" width="2087" height="796" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/talks.jpg 2087w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/talks-360x137.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/talks-768x293.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/talks-1024x391.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2087px) 100vw, 2087px" /></p>
<p>活动同时将通过 Prada 官方微信小程序直播，现在已经可以开始预约。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1361391" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/631b0c55ly1gi30xjnuw1j20u03qt7mc-3.jpg" alt="" width="1043" height="530" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/631b0c55ly1gi30xjnuw1j20u03qt7mc-3.jpg 1043w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/631b0c55ly1gi30xjnuw1j20u03qt7mc-3-360x183.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/631b0c55ly1gi30xjnuw1j20u03qt7mc-3-768x390.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/631b0c55ly1gi30xjnuw1j20u03qt7mc-3-1024x520.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1043px) 100vw, 1043px" /></p>
